<div class="container">
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Wedding Information</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="info-elements row justify-content-center">

    <div class="wedding-image col-12 col-lg-6">
      <%= image_tag "garden.jpg", alt: "alttext" %>
    </div>

    <div class="address col-12 col-lg-6">
      <h1>Saturday 17 July 2021</h1>
      <br>
      <h3>Bells Forstal Farmhouse</h3>
      <h3>Throwley</h3>
      <h3>Faversham</h3>
      <h3>Kent</h3>
      <h3>ME13 0JS</h3>
      <br>
    </div>

   </div>


   <div class="travel-elements row">
    <div class="travel-info col-12 col-lg-6">
      <h3><center>Travel</center></h3>
      <br>
      <h6><strong>Throwley is a 10-15 minute taxi ride from Faversham or Charing train stations</strong></h6>
      <br>
      <h5><strong>Trains</strong></h5>
      <h6>London St Pancras to Faversham around 1 hour / to Charing (via Ashford) 50 minutes.</h6>
      <h6>London Victoria to Faversham 1 hour 15 mins / to Charing around 1 hour 30 minutes.</h6>
      <br>
      <h5><strong>Taxis must be booked in advance</strong></h5>
      <h6>Starlite Taxis: 01795 591066</h6>
      <h6>Reeves Taxis: 01795 536666</h6>
      <br>
      <h5><strong>Return coach to London</strong></h5>
      <h6>We are organising a coach from the wedding to London at the end of the evening.</h6>
      <h6> Please contact us as soon as possible if you are interested at <a href="mailto:tkandruby@gmail.com">tkandruby@gmail.com</a></h6>
    </div>

    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6" id="map"
     style="width: 500px; height: 500px;"
     data-markers="<%= @markers.to_json %>"
     data-mapbox-api-key="<%= ENV['MAPBOX_API_KEY'] %>">
     </div>
   </div>

  <div class="gifts-elements row">

    <div class="gift-image col-12 col-lg-6">
      <%= image_tag "nancy_bruno.jpg", alt: "alttext" %>
    </div>

    <div class="gifts-info col-sm-12 col-lg-6">
      <h3><center>Gifts</center></h3>
      <br>
      <h5>Your presence at our wedding is enough of a gift!</h5>
      <br>
      <h6>However, if you would still like to give a gift, we would be grateful for any contributions to our honeymoon fund. We will be going to Italy in 2022!</h6>
      <br>
      <div class="contact">
        <p>If you have any questions at all, please don't hesitate to get in touch with us at <a href="mailto:tkandruby@gmail.com">tkandruby@gmail.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>

   </div>
   <br>
</div>
</div>


